One way to solve this is with streaming token-parsing with Gson. This method handles extremely large JSON strings with ease.

Example before and after:

    {&quot;a&quot;:{&quot;removeme&quot;:&quot;unwanted&quot;,&quot;b&quot;:{&quot;c&quot;:{&quot;removeme&quot;:{&quot;x&quot;:1},&quot;d&quot;:{&quot;e&quot;:123}}}}}
